oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Interior of barber shop
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Interior view of a barber shop and shoe shine parlor. There are two men getting haircuts and one of the men is getting a shoe shine from an employee. Five employees of the barber shop are standing behind the chairs.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Barbershops; Barbers' chairs; Shoe shiners
